Agenda : Anaconda installation process:
=======================================
   Meaning of Anaconda :
   --------------------
      Anaconda is an open-source software that contains Jupyter, spyder, etc that are used for large data processing, data analytics, heavy scientific computing. 
      Anaconda works for R and python programming language. Spyder(sub-application of Anaconda) is used for python. Opencv for python will work in spyder. 
      Package versions are managed by the package management system called conda.

    Learn more about Anaconda :
    ---------------------------
       https://freelearning.anaconda.cloud/get-started-with-anaconda
   
   Anaconda installation process : 
   ------------------------------- 
      To begin working with Anaconda, one must get it installed first. Follow the below instructions to Download and install Anaconda on your system:
      > Folllow this Doc : https://freelearning.anaconda.cloud/get-started-with-anaconda/18199 
         > Switched to this site : https://www.anaconda.com/download/success 
         > Choose Your OS : I am choose downlod option for windows.
         > Once Download is complete
         > Go to download path open the anaconda installer, Click on next, next until finish.

   
